.TH "CITADEL" "1" "Jul 2026" "AceTeam" "Citadel CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
citadel-update-disable - Disable automatic updates


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel update disable [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Disables automatic updates. Takes effect on a running 'citadel work'
agent within one check interval, without a restart.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for disable


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable colorized output


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBcitadel-update(1)\fP
